 years to come, engaging and delighting both general readers and food professionals.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCooking (Pasta) 0aCooking (Pasta)xItaly. 0aCooking (Pasta). 0aPasta productsxEncyclopediasxItaly. 0aPasta productsxHistoryxItaly. 0aPasta productszItalyvEncyclopedias. 0aPasta productszItalyxHistory. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Agriculture & Food (see also POLITICAL SCIENCE / Public Policy / Agriculture & Food Policy).2bisacsh  acookbook.  acookbooks italian.  acooking.  afamily recipes.  afood and culture.  afood and diet.  afood lovers.  afood prep.  afood reference.  afood scholars.  afood.  ageographical.  agnocchi.  ahistorical.  ahistory of food.  ahistory of pasta.  ahome cooks.  aillustrated.  aitalian pasta.  aitaly.  akitchen setting.  amediterranean foods.  anonfiction.  aoral histories.  apasta lovers.  apasta recipes.  apasta.  apreparation techniques.  aravioli.  aregional cuisine.  aspaghetti.  astaple food.  astrascinati.  atagliatelle.  avincisgrassi.1 aBarberis, Corrado, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFant, Maureen B, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aField, Carol, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZanini De Vita, Oretta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094471840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520944718423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520944718/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-